<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>XARO | Écosystème Business</title>
    <style>
        /* --- STYLE GLOBAL XARO --- */
        :root {
            --primary: #ff6a00; /* Orange XARO puissant */
            --bg-dark: #050505;
            --bg-card: #0d0d0d;
            --text-white: #ffffff;
            --text-gray: #777777;
            --glow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.3);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-white);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* --- NAVIGATION --- */
        nav {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            padding: 25px 8%;
            background: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.95);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #151515;
            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .logo span { color: var(--primary); }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-white); text-decoration: none; margin-left: 25px;
            font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); }

        /* --- SECTION HÉROS --- */
        .hero {
            height: 80vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #151515 0%, #050505 100%);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff 30%, #444 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero p { color: var(--text-gray); max-width: 500px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }

        .btn-main {
            background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 18px 45px;
            text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px; font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;
            box-shadow: var(--glow); transition: 0.4s;
        }

        .btn-main:hover { transform: scale(1.05); background: white; color: black; box-shadow: 0 0 40px white; }

        /* --- SECTION SERVICES --- */
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 100px 20px; }
        
        .services-grid {
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--bg-card); padding: 45px; border-radius: 0px;
            border: 1px solid #151515; transition: 0.3s;
            text-align: left; text-decoration: none; color: white;
        }

        .card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); background: #000; }

        .card h3 { color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .card p { color: var(--text-gray); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        footer {
            text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px; color: #333;
            border-top: 1px solid #111; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">XA<span>RO</span></div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">Solutions</a>
            <a href="#">Réseau</a>
            <a href="#">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>XARO CORP.</h1>
        <p>L'excellence technologique. La puissance du réseau. Le futur de votre business commence ici.</p>
        <a href="#services" class="btn-main">Entrer dans le réseau</a>
    </section>

    <div class="container" id="services">
        <div class="services-grid">
            
            <a href="#" class="card">
                <h3>XARO Digital</h3>
                <p>Développement de plateformes haute performance et infrastructures web sécurisées.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="card">
                <h3>XARO Market</h3>
                <p>Accès exclusif à nos outils propriétaires et ressources premium pour entreprises.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="card">
                <h3>XARO Network</h3>
                <p>Connectez-vous à une communauté d'élite et développez vos partenariats stratégiques.</p>
            </a>

        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 XARO CORPORATION. TOUS DROITS RÉSERVÉS.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
